                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding contemporary="true">
                        <p>Fifteenth-century ruled and stamped binding with cut-leather decoration (the Virgin and Child) on the upper board. Contemporary labels on the upper board with contents and pressmark.</p>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
